{"tid":1061769,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"hollow knight 出咗實體版","createTime":"2019-03-14T15:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T15:32:55.000Z","uid":134437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8fd8084717e2f7d8601a2bbf993d3caae6d340a","tid":1061769,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"有ns, ps4 and PC<br />\ncollector's edition PC/PS4:$64, NS:$69<br />\nstandard edition PC/PS4:$29, NS:$34<br />\n<br />\nfangamer有<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fangamer.com/products/hollow-knight-switch-ps4-pc-game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fangamer.com%2Fproducts%2Fhollow-knight-switch-ps4-pc-game&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpnocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=c2a24684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fangamer.com/products/hollow-knight-switch-ps4-pc-game</a><br />\n<br />\nHollow Knight Standard &amp; Collector&rsquo;s Edition Now Available To Preorder At Fangamer<br />\n<br />\nHollow Knight fans will surely be overjoyed now that, finally, a Hollow Knight physical edition is a reality!<br />\n<br />\nFollowing an ESRB rating for the game last month, Hollow Knight will now be getting a standard and collector&rsquo;s editions for Switch.<br />\n<br />\nThe Collector&rsquo;s Edition includes:<br />\n<br />\nMetal brooch with display stand, wall hook, and dual-pronged fastener<br />\n14-page Quirrel comic book<br />\nGift-box-style case with gold-foil filigree and a clear printed sleeve<br />\nGold-foil art print set by Ari Gibson<br />\nPhysical copy of the game on your choice of platform including all DLC: Hidden Dreams, The Grimm Troupe, Lifeblood, and Godmaster.<br />\nNintendo Switch&trade; copies of the Collector&rsquo;s Edition include a bonus cleaning cloth<br />\nMeanwhile, all editions of the game will include an instruction manual and fold-out map of Hallownest.<br />\n<br />\nstandard edition<br />\n<img src=\"https://nintendosoup.com/?attachment_id